title: Week 7: All-NMPreps.com Football Team
text:
Week 7: All-NMPreps.com Football Team Kyle Henderson Talk about it in NEW MEXICO PREP FOOTBALL INSIDER 
Each Tuesday on NMPreps.com we select the All-New Mexico Team based off weekly performances. The All-New Mexico Team is selected by NMPreps.com is powered by Stoven Construction, Inc. 
Allan Rodriguez of Volcano Vista High School came up with a big interception against Cibola last Friday Night. On the year he has 4 interceptions. Offense 
QB - Orlando Perez - Manzano - Threw for 100-yards, ran for 134-yards returned kickoff 74-yards for a touchdown against Sandia. QB - Marcos Gonzales West Mesa; 186 passing with 3TD's, 176 Rushing yards with 3 TD's, and 1 interception on Defense. Total of 6 TD's against Valley RB - Ethan Duff - Artesia - Ran for 152-yards, 50-yards receiving against Alamogordo
